data.name: txtInstructions.Text
data.value:
Instructions:
Enter a 5-letter word into the text box below. When you press "Guess," it will appear here.
If a letter has a Green Square around it, then it is the correct letter in the correct location If a letter has a Yellow Square around it, then it is a correct letter, but in the wrong location If a letter has a Grey Square around it, then that letter does not appear in the word. HINT: There are no plural nouns.
You have 6 guesses to figure out what the word is. Good Luck!
